OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers, these
OL,8,Fbecoming fewer and increasingly
OL,9,Fconfined to northern parts and the
OL,10,FIsles. Touch of frost in sheltered
OL,11,Fparts. Winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA few showers, mainly around
OL,14,Fcoastal areas, and sunny spells, the
OL,15,Fbest of these towards the Great Glen
OL,16,Fand the south. Occasionally fresh
OL,17,Fnorthwesterly winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
