OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright morning Saturday but cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing with rain in west later.
OL,8,FRain spreading east overnight,
OL,9,Fclearing Sunday morning with showers
OL,10,Ffollowing. Rather cloudy Monday with
OL,11,Foccasional rain. Becoming milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
